OL,3,CVolunteers 'heartbroken' after 30,000
OL,4,Cnewly planted bulbs mowed down by
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FA community group in Bristol which
OL,8,Fplanted 30,000 bulbs in a park have
OL,9,Fbeen left "heartbroken" after the
OL,10,Fcouncil mowed them down days later.
OL,12,FThe Friends of St George Park raised
OL,13,F#6,000 by selling duck food to fund
OL,14,Fthe project and says members were
OL,15,Fadvised by Bristol City Council about
OL,16,Fwhat to plant and where.
OL,18,FBristol City Council say it is
OL,19,Finvestigating what happened.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@WO]
