OL,3,CVolunteers 'heartbroken' after 30,000
OL,4,Cnewly planted bulbs mowed down by
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FMore than 70 volunteers, including
OL,8,Fseveral families and children, came to
OL,9,Fhelp on Saturday 7th March in what was
OL,10,Fdescribed as "the biggest project
OL,11,Fwe've ever done". Among them were two
OL,12,Fcouncillors from the Green Party.
OL,14,FAilie Tam, from the group, says the
OL,15,Fplanting was planned for months and
OL,16,Fwas part of a wider plan to enhance
OL,17,Fhabitats in the park. They were also
OL,18,Fadvised by two ecologists.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773418278
OL,3,CVolunteers 'heartbroken' after 30,000
OL,4,Cnewly planted bulbs mowed down by
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FBut days later the area by St George
OL,8,FLibrary was mowed over by contractors
OL,9,Fdamaging, and likely destroying, the
OL,10,Fnewly planted bulbs.
OL,12,FAilie said: "It's heartbreaking and
OL,13,Freally frustrating. It's like taking a
OL,14,Fstep forward and two steps back.
OL,16,F"All the hard work, energy, the morale
OL,17,Fand the community spirit - it's
OL,18,Fbeggar's belief that it's happened.
OL,26,@tD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773418278
OL,3,CVolunteers 'heartbroken' after 30,000
OL,4,Cnewly planted bulbs mowed down by
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"Just really disheartened and gutted
OL,8,Foverall. It just feels like a waste. A
OL,9,Fwaste of time, energy, and plants.
OL,10,FIt's a waste."
OL,12,FAilie is hopeful some of the bulbs,
OL,13,Fwhich included native flowers like
OL,14,Fsnowdrops, daffodils, bluebells, and
OL,15,Fwild garlic, may still recover.
OL,17,FShe said: "Some of the bulbs will
OL,18,Fhopefully recover.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
