OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773418278
OL,3,CVolunteers 'heartbroken' after 30,000
OL,4,Cnewly planted bulbs mowed down by
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"We wanted flowers this spring but
OL,8,Fthat is not going to happen. Some will
OL,9,Fcome back next year but for others the
OL,10,Fcollateral damage means that they
OL,11,Fwon't recover."
OL,13,FBristol City Council say the Head of
OL,14,FService is investigating the
OL,15,Fcircumstances around this.
OL,26,@sD@OO]
